---
title: Apricot-Glazed Beef Meatballs with Potato Fries & Carrot Slaw
description: Your favourite plump little orange fruit has been turned into a sauce and wrapped around tender chermoula-spiced beef meatballs to add a burst of sweetness. Paired with classic potato fries and a crunchy slaw, you can’t go wrong!
